{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People coming from other camps into the hospital, they bring the lice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were so much lice you cannot imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course I had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When, when, when you had a, a belt and the lice hard for them to get through the belt, you could just go around the belt and have nearly a handful of it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, in inside Allach when winter came, well, I didn't know my father died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just went, went in beginning of December to, to that place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Started getting cold nights and started snowing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found two big heaps of potato, which was actually for us, put into straw for freeze-- not freezing, inside the camp territory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About three, four meters high, like a pyramid shape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And covered with earth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- each time they had to use 200, 300 kilo, they opened it up and they pulled it out and they put it back when one gets frozen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So 5 o'clock in the morning, I got up with a few more young chaps and we went and started pinching potatoes there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We opened up where it was half closed and soft.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we put the potatoes on steel wire, one after the other, and put it through the chimney.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the barrack had a-- the room where the capo lived, a small room where the head of the barrack lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he used to fire his little stove.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we let it in from the roof top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was snow covered already, the roof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you had to watch if, if the guards want-- sometimes they put projectors around, going in circles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the projector wasn't on, climb up on the roof, let the potato singe, leave it in for about 30 minutes.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
